(Helical Hole Pattern)
G21 ; Set units to millimeters
G90 ; Absolute positioning

(Safe Move to Zero)
G0 Z5.0 ; 1. Raise Z to safe travel height
G0 X0.000 Y0.000 ; 2. Move X and Y to Work Zero
G0 Z0.000 ; 3. Lower Z to the surface (Optional, just to verify zero)
G0 Z5.0 ; 4. Retract back to safe height before starting

